lines.text: [On a gondola, in a canal, in Venice, Italy]
How long the streets been fucked up like this?

[Lira is singing an aria while having sex with Bobby]
I used to be able to fuck like that.

[Lira and Eddie are singing in a performance of 'Otello']
You have a limp noodle!
Hi, I'm Jack Fine and this is my suicidal son, Bobby.
